# Executive Portfolio – Abhimanyu Kariganur

A modern, mobile‑responsive personal branding site showcasing governance, compliance, automation, and digital transformation leadership. Built to support **Senior Manager / Director applications, consulting engagements, international opportunities, expert networks, and LinkedIn credibility**.

## 🌟 Features
- Directive **Executive Dashboard** with key business impact metrics  
- **Global Availability Map** showing openness to international roles  
- **Executive Case Studies**: DOFRC, Project Bad Address, Learning Minds, Automation, Transition, Risk Controls, Escalation Matrix, Pre‑Live QA, Outside Trustee Recordkeeping  
- **AI & Digital Transformation** section highlighting modern tools and hackathon participation  
- **Certifications & Recognition** including PMP (in progress), QKA, Design Thinking, Values Champion, Inclusivity Champion  
- **Dark/Light Theme Toggle** and **Mobile Responsive Design**  
- **Downloadable Resume (PDF)** for recruiters  

